Quarter: The fiscal quarter for which the compliance audit data is reported, formatted as 'QX YYYY'.
Audit_Cost_Percentage: Compliance audit cost as a percentage of the annual revenue for the specified quarter.
Audit_Cost_Total: Total cost of the compliance audit for the specified quarter, in US dollars.
Annual_Revenue: The total annual revenue of Elexion Automotive, in US dollars.
Revenue_Range: The range of the annual revenue for Elexion Automotive, given as a descriptive range (e.g., '$350M - $500M').
Compliance_Certifications: List of compliance certifications relevant to the audit, separated by commas.
